channel.title: I Need Help With -Fedexer-'s TUT!
channel.description:
Hello,
As I'm sure a lot of you know about -Fedexer-'s TUT that he made. The one about deleting global objects? Sure you do. Anyway I'm sure I'm not the only one to have added that to my server because it seems to be pretty popular.
However there is a problem that I, and a few other people, are having trouble with. After you delete a good amount of World Objects it can create a serious amount of lag. If anybody has found a solution to this problem, it would be greatly appreciated if you would post the solution. Please help, because I'm sure that I'm not the only one looking for the answer to this problem!
(BTW -Fedexer- it is a great TUT and I did post on your thread!)
